'''Former members'''
* [[Vince Clarke]]{{nbsp}}– keyboards, lead and backing vocals, guitars (1980–1981)
* [[Alan Wilder]]{{nbsp}}– keyboards, piano, drums, backing vocals (1982–1995; one-off show in 2010)

